  - distance between people is no longer shown in steps, but feet.

  - If you encounter any bugs or typos please write down some info with the
    'bug' and 'typo' command, thanks
  
  - debug is now enabled in some /base files, so you will receive an error
    if some object is missing any value.

  - there is now an lpc-ftpd, using port 3337
    login name is no longer tta.<username>, now only <username>
